Note on source data (NOT covered by this dedication):

The population statistics and boundary data used to generate the maps are
provided by third parties and remain subject to their own terms of use:

- 国勢調査（人口速報集計・小地域集計）: 総務省統計局 / e-Stat
- 国土数値情報 行政区域データ（N03, 2020年版および大正9年=1920年版）: 国土交通省
- 背景地図（地理院タイル）: 国土地理院

CC0 waives only the rights of this repository's author(s). It does not and
cannot waive any rights held by the providers of the source data above. When
reusing the data or derived layers, keep the appropriate source attribution.
